scripts.git-proxy: git config --global http.proxy "http://127.0.0.1:7890" && git config --global https.proxy "http://127.0.0.1:7890"
scripts.git-unproxy: git config --global --unset http.proxy  && git config --global --unset https.proxy
scripts.git-push: npm run git-proxy && git push origin master && npm run git-unproxy
